data.enText: a person, a country or an organization that has signed an official agreement
data.chText: （协议的）签署者，签署方，签署国

data.enText: a signatory of the Declaration of Independence
Many countries are signatories to/of the Berne Convention.
data.chText: 很多国家都是《伯尔尼公约》的签署国。

means: (协议的)签署者，签署方，签署国

tr: someone who signs and is bound by a document

example.ex: Both countries are signatories to the Nuclear Non-Proliferation Treaty.
example.tran: 两个国家都是《核不扩散条约》的签约国。

value.def: The signatories of an official document are the people, organizations, or countries that have signed it.
value.tran: (正式文件的)签署人，签署方，签约国
